data.text: Rolo Tomassi is a British progressive metal band from Sheffield. They have been active since 2005 and their new record, Where Myth Becomes Memory, is their sixth full-length album. It is the follow up to their critically acclaimed 2018 album, Time Will Die And Love Will Bury It. The group is known for their sonic and energetic live performances, as well as their stark and consistent artistic aesthetic.
